                                               Churn Rate by Contract Type

                              Business Question
What is our churn rate for each contract type?

                         QUERY
SELECT 
    Contract,
    COUNT(*) Total_customer,
    SUM(CASE WHEN Customer_Status = 'Churned' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS churned_customers,
    ROUND(
        CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN Customer_Status = 'Churned' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS FLOAT) * 100 / COUNT(*),
        2
    ) AS churn_rate
FROM telecom_customer
GROUP BY Contract

